
  Syntax:	cast 'fireball'
  Damage:	1d30 for every level up to level 20
    Type:	Fire
    Area:	Yes
   Touch:	No
    Cost:	80 Mana
MinSpeed:	Short
    Save:	vs. fire for half damage

This spell will bring into existance a magical explosion that inflicts
firedamage to livings within its area of effect.

